title: 11/04/21 DPS Hour 2 Ross Tucker
itunes:title: 11/04/21 DPS Hour 2 Ross Tucker
description:
Former NFL player and host of the "Ross Tucker Football Podcast" Ross Tucker joins The Dan Patrick Show to discuss the Packers chances of winning this weekend without Aaron Rodgers and explains why Rodgers "personal decision" about getting vaccinated isn't really a personal decision.
